{"tid":1501002,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實連登根本就係社會小眾，呢個平台根本無撚用","createTime":"2019-08-24T08:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T14:36:25.000Z","uid":134134,"like":39,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f563c174c553344a8c1e590ef5ed3d318419a3be","tid":1501002,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:19:29.000Z","msg":"個個話支持做嘢嗰啲組織，支持攬炒巴，我聽完得啖笑。<br />\n成日想世界關注，又得個講字，個個剩係識喺連登推post，推到上熱門都無美國佬知啦。<br />\n有NY Times 嗰外媒主動幫你整youtube片，唔幫手推都算。連StandwithHK個channel都無人subscribe like comment，結果連香港熱門都上唔到，上到吹水台熱門都無撚用啦。<br />\n截至24/8/2019 1551，StandwithHK嘅訂閱數只係「2.6萬」，而最多觀看次數嘅一條片只係「250,865次」。比對一下所謂大波差婆IG，追隨人數短短幾日就由800升到「20.8k」，同少波子同期喺7月中上載嘅片嘅「403,214次」。<br />\n聽完個數字，你哋可唔可恥呀<span style=\"color: red;\">和理廢</span>？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持咗先得2.6萬，所以話連登根本係社會小眾，呢個平台根本無撚用。<br />\n-------------------------------------------<br />\nStandwithHK youtube channel：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=a3cc34fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw</a><br />\nThe NewYork Times youtube channel：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqnbDFdCpuN8CMEg0VuEBqA?sub_confirmation=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCqnbDFdCpuN8CMEg0VuEBqA%3Fsub_confirmation%3D1&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=d7ae861b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqnbDFdCpuN8CMEg0VuEBqA?sub_confirmation=1</a><br />\nStandwithHK twitter：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=554f3e7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK</a><br />\nReddit r/worldnews：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/worldnews/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fworldnews%2F&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=a77c9230\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reddit.com/r/worldnews/</a>"},{"pid":"99381a54b34ee450431fcc0040a62abe051e4454","tid":1501002,"uid":134134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:23:22.000Z","msg":"【現存白宮聯署更新】<br />\n<br />\n明白現在實在太多白宮聯署，好多人會唔記得自己簽咗邊個，我有以下建議：<br />\n<br />\n1/ 唔肯定嘅，簽多一次。在我的道德標準下，呢個可以，因為你唔係故意用同一個電郵簽幾次。<br />\n<br />\n2/ 簽咗之後，自己mark返自己簽咗邊個，這是大家的責任。<br />\n<br />\n《未夠數》<br />\n==========<br />\n中國武警冒充香港警察，白宮聯署請求美國國會盡快通過香港人權民主法案 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YW8pa8&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=664a5035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國取消中國學生簽證<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30GcBMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30GcBMM&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=5cd6b8ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30GcBMM</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民<br />\n�<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KsmYOQ&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=d742da85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國將中國共產黨定性為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MlpLM3&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=c49f0ac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國向北京施壓，停止製造白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Zkc8hX&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=b51e0923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX</a><br />\n<br />\n拯救國泰航空，保障經濟自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZmWgPU&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=22ab95b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU</a><br />\n<br />\n要求拒絕前警務處處長曾偉雄到聯合國就任提名<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Z0cMkw&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=a1fa3e5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw</a><br />\n🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n《以下夠數，但到期前越多人越好》<br />\n==========<br />\n請求美國派出醫療船支援香港�<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2H221Iu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H221Iu&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=f51b8693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2H221Iu</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國國會確認香港警察為恐怖組織�<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KzVVQB&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=816ba415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB</a><br />\n<br />\n請美國國會提名【爭取民主自由的香港人】競逐諾貝爾和平獎，藉以保護義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZbGdQH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZbGdQH&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=0c7cf0d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZbGdQH</a><br />\n<br />\n簽名＞等電郵＞確認簽名＞傳開去<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/archuoic/?epa=SEARCH_BOX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Farchuoic%2F%3Fepa%3DSEARCH_BOX&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=5d8729e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/archuoic/?epa=SEARCH_BOX</a>"},{"pid":"422f79818075619aa76432c6f40e70a42d00a514","tid":1501002,"uid":295662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f563c174c553344a8c1e590ef5ed3d31841